TopicTitle: Huge frame drop when loading even 1 part in VAB

Articles.Content:
Hey,

When i'm in the VAB and load even 1 part, my FPS drops from 80 to 10. I'm using Realism Overhaul. I'm using latest KSP in OpenGL. 

The console is being spammed with
